{"tid":1099724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大角嘴洗衣店遭撬閘爆竊 賊人抬走收銀機失數百現金","createTime":"2019-04-10T03:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T04:00:33.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"da51b7b00457d1869aae12a2abddc51990657839","tid":1099724,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/adAvfjX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FadAvfjX.png&h=d99d9600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洗衣店被爆竊，警員到場調查。梁澤岡攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZqSQZMH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZqSQZMH.png&h=333ba950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YRVOMrR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYRVOMrR.png&h=fc4c8b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n收銀機被抬走。梁澤岡攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWygVkY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWygVkY.png&h=ce635d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賊人撬開電閘蓋潛入爆竊。梁澤岡攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UVayXzm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUVayXzm.png&h=90dc8716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洗衣店被爆竊，警員到場翻看cctv調查。梁澤岡攝<br />\n<br />\n大角嘴角祥街71號地下一間洗衣店，早上9時56分，女店東返回開舖，發現店舖捲閘升起約1米，內有搜掠痕迹，收銀機不翼而飛，報警求助，警員到場調查事件，相信賊人撬毀電閘蓋潛入爆竊。女店東初步點算損失約數百元，警方正翻查cctv追緝賊人。"},{"pid":"c050f3e8f59a9ec44739f2d29e557629ed1f6608","tid":1099724,"uid":88491,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:17:23.000Z","msg":"搞咁多野偷得幾百蚊 想睇下個賊個表情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec7387abbe9a96fe026e9e5b7639d2b1a628be8","tid":1099724,"uid":227275,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:21:11.000Z","msg":"比d大志喇屌"},{"pid":"61cadb559d9aa9e9e63cb7e3a35d400b3c2115bb","tid":1099724,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03